{%- comment -%} ── Why Valor pillars ──────────────────────────────────── {%- endcomment -%}
<section class="vr-pillars">
  <div class="vr-pillars-inner">
    <div class="vr-pillars-head">
      <div class="vr-eyebrow">Why Valor</div>
      <div class="vr-pillars-title">29 years in the industry. <em>And counting.</em></div>
      <p class="vr-pillars-intro">We've been shipping wireless accessories from Los Angeles since 1997. Through every device cycle from flip phones to foldables, our partners have grown with a single source they trust to deliver — on time, on margin, and ready before the next launch.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="vr-pillars-grid">
      <div class="vr-pillar">
        <div class="vr-pillar-num">01</div>
        <h3 class="vr-pillar-title">Always one step ahead.</h3>
        <p>We engineer accessories for new devices before they're officially announced. By the time a phone hits retail, our cases, screen protectors, and chargers are already in your warehouse. Partners don't wait for "soon" — they reorder for what's already shipping.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="vr-pillar">
        <div class="vr-pillar-num">02</div>
        <h3 class="vr-pillar-title">Factory to shelf, no detours.</h3>
        <p>We own our manufacturing, our R&amp;D, and 250,000 sq ft of bicoastal distribution across LA and Texas. No middlemen, no contract-manufacturer surprises. The mold, the unit, the carton, the truck — all under one roof.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="vr-pillar">
        <div class="vr-pillar-num">03</div>
        <h3 class="vr-pillar-title">More than a vendor.</h3>
        <p>Wide selection across every category, brand, and device. Trends caught before they're trends. And a dedicated rep who knows your channel, picks up the phone, and helps you make it land.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{%- comment -%} ── Apply CTA (dark) ───────────────────────────────────── {%- endcomment -%}
<section class="vr-cta">
  <div class="vr-cta-inner">
    <div class="vr-cta-left">
      <div class="vr-cta-eyebrow">Become a Valor partner</div>
      <div class="vr-cta-title">Your accessory to <em>success.</em></div>
      <p class="vr-cta-body">Register for a free account to unlock wholesale pricing, place orders, and access the full Valor catalog. You'll get marketing kits with every SKU, fast bicoastal shipping, flexible payment options, and a dedicated rep who knows your channel.</p>
      <div class="vr-cta-actions">
        <button type="button" class="vr-btn vr-btn--chalk" data-vr-open>
          Apply for an account
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
        </button>
        <a class="vr-btn vr-btn--outline js-shopify-login-trigger">Sign in to existing account</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="vr-cta-right">
      <div class="vr-cta-grid">
        {%- assign cta_items = '16,000+ active SKUs|Across all major carriers, brands & product lines;Zero MOQ on stocked SKUs|Order by the unit, not by the case;Fast bicoastal shipping|Same-day from LA & Texas DCs;Flexible payment options|Net terms, credit card, Apple Pay, and PayPal;Marketing kit per SKU|Photography, copy, sell sheets, and short-form video;A real human in your corner|Dedicated rep who knows your channel and picks up the phone' | split: ';' -%}
        {%- for item in cta_items -%}
          {%- assign parts = item | split: '|' -%}
          <div class="vr-cta-item">
            <span class="vr-cta-star" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 .587l3.668 7.568L24 9.423l-6 5.851L19.336 24 12 19.897 4.664 24 6 15.274 0 9.423l8.332-1.268z"/></svg>
            </span>
            <div>
              <div class="vr-cta-item-title">{{ parts[0] }}</div>
              <div class="vr-cta-item-sub">{{ parts[1] }}</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        {%- endfor -%}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

